{"word":"Tophet","slug":"tophet","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tophet</b> <a href=\"#/H8612\">H8612</a><br/><a href=\"#/H8613\">H8613</a> <br/> Called also Topheth.<br/> A place in the valley of the sons of Hinnom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a><br/> Jewish children passed through the fire to Molech in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=32'>Jer 7:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=6'>Jer 19:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=14'>Jer 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=35'>Jer 32:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=3'>2Ch 28:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=33&verse=6'>2Ch 33:6</a><br/> Destroyed by Josiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a><br/> Horror of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=33'>Isa 30:33</a>"}]}